# Changelog
All notable changes to SLACK CLONE project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
- Starred Component to Favorite  Unfavorite Channels
- MetaPanel Component to Display Channel Info
- Color Picker to Change App Colors
- Change and Edit User Avatar Images
- Display Animation when Users Typing
- Adding Emoji Picker, Loading Skeleton, Automatic Scroll to Bottom, Key Shortcuts
- Removing Listeners, Securing our App with Firebase Rules
- Deploying our App with Firebase Tools

## [1.0.1] - 2021-21-01
### Added
- Add changelog file
### Changed
- Update .gitignore file for remove yarn.lock
- Update package.json for added engine to vercel app
- Update action types, reducers with private channel between user
- Update action types with private channel between user
- Update sidepanel with channel's notification counter unread message (new message)
- Update sidepanel directmessage component for active menu user on private channel change
- Update update message component display references and header for public and private channel
- Update variable in context app component for boolean isPrivateChannel
- Update messageform component with reference updload and send message 